{"tid":1786394,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滿州獨立都有被捕師 「旅外學者返回中國被捕 疑鼓吹滿獨被鎖定」","createTime":"2019-12-17T06:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T06:56:00.000Z","uid":292987,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ceac05703d3528bfdbd30d0bb0a9a30f605b4b55","tid":1786394,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201912170108.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201912170108.aspx&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0vo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=62363bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201912170108.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者楊昇儒台北17日電）旅居芬蘭從事博士後研究的環保學者王展，10月返回中國被警方以「煽動顛覆國家政權罪」刑拘。有消息指他疑似因為鼓吹「滿洲獨立」被中共鎖定。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好以為唔講獨立，支共就搵唔到位入啦。滿洲咁小眾嘅主張都拉咗。<br />\n<br />\n話時話，依家戰火燒遍支那，又圖博又東突，又台灣又香港，滿蒙都入埋來。我哋唔可以俾支共唞到氣！香港人，盡做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9409b337fa4ee9a12f85521342a7170d0077eace","tid":1786394,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ec4a90d89e8e5ba76d0292d7f3e4fcd31e5a5c","tid":1786394,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:14:18.000Z","msg":"香港金總終於接受網上會員申請啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fbb9d2e0169afdac77f96f46dd32097ca3803536","tid":1786394,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:14:59.000Z","msg":"p牌係咪冇得自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3455c32f9ae05c465192fbedf47d80c8d6c8af4a","tid":1786394,"uid":143241,"li